                Use type of `uint2`, `uint3` for higher dimension. Then use x = index.x, y = index.y. 
                Each index is assigned to individual thread to perform concurrently.
                
                @Code(name: "Metal File", file: Calculation3.metal)
            }
            
            @Step {
                Define the input array.
                
                Arrays and mutable variables are passed as arguments. Passing constants will be introduced later.
                
